### Add product
POST http://localhost:8080/product-management/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "name" : "Black Shorts",
  "price" : "30.99"
}

### Update product
PUT http://localhost:8080/product-management/products/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "name" : "Blue Shorts",
  "price" : "20.00"
}

### Find product
GET http://localhost:8080/product-management/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Find all products
GET http://localhost:8080/product-management/products
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Delete product
DELETE http://localhost:8080/product-management/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}